      <title>气候受到威胁的图瓦卢举行选举，中国台湾关注</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/climate-threatened-tuvalu-holds-election-watched-by-taiwan-china-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，太平洋小岛国图瓦卢的全国选举投票开始，中国、台湾、美国及其盟友澳大利亚都在密切关注这场选举，以争夺该地区的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/climate-threatened-tuvalu-holds-election-watched-by-taiwan-china-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 03:06:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士信贷前亚太区资产管理主管退出瑞银 - 消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/former-credit-suisse-apac-asset-management-head-exiting-ubs-sources-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位知情人士称，瑞信亚太区前资产管理主管黄敏将离开瑞银，因为瑞银在全球领导层变动后开始审查其中国业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/former-credit-suisse-apac-asset-management-head-exiting-ubs-sources-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 02:37:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数千人举行“入侵日”集会抗议澳大利亚国庆日假期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-protest-australia-day-holiday-with-invasion-day-rallies-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多澳大利亚原住民（占该国 2600 万人口的 3.8%）拒绝接受这个节日，认为它标志着自欧洲殖民以来所遭受的不公正的开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thousands-protest-australia-day-holiday-with-invasion-day-rallies-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 02:22:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市有望每周上涨；关注美国通胀测试</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周五将结束连续三周的下跌，而投资者则等待当天晚些时候美国通胀的关键数据，以评估美国利率的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 02:17:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫沙利文将在曼谷会见中国外交部长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/white-houses-sullivan-meet-with-chinas-foreign-minister-bangkok-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文将于周五和周六在曼谷会见中国外交部长王毅，以两国领导人深化世界两大经济体之间对话的承诺为基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/white-houses-sullivan-meet-with-chinas-foreign-minister-bangkok-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 02:02:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾12月贸易逆差40亿美元，创四个月新低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/philippines-posts-4-bln-trade-deficit-december-four-month-low-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府周五公布的数据显示，菲律宾 12 月份贸易逆差为 40.1 亿美元，为四个月以来的最小逆差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/philippines-posts-4-bln-trade-deficit-december-four-month-low-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 01:17:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰撤回允许16岁青少年在地方机构选举中投票的法案</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-withdraws-bill-allowing-16-year-olds-vote-local-body-elections-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰政府周五撤回了一项法案，如果该法案获得通过，该法案将允许 16 岁的青少年在地方政府选举中投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-withdraws-bill-allowing-16-year-olds-vote-local-body-elections-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 01:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电池制造商 LG Energy Solution 预计全球电动汽车市场放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/battery-firm-lg-energy-solutions-q4-profit-up-43-higher-us-output-2024-01-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国电池制造商 LG Energy Solution (LGES) 周五预测，今年全球电动汽车 (EV) 市场增长将放缓，这表明在中国竞争对手加剧的竞争中，未来将面临进一步的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/battery-firm-lg-energy-solutions-q4-profit-up-43-higher-us-output-2024-01-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 00:27:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>热带气旋过后，数千名澳大利亚人断电</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/thousands-australians-without-power-tropical-cyclone-aftermath-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，热带气旋夜间袭击澳大利亚昆士兰州，带来破坏性大风和暴雨，导致数万人断电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/thousands-australians-without-power-tropical-cyclone-aftermath-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 23:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 的 Altman 将于周五会见芯片制造商三星和 SK 海力士高管 - 消息人士</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/openais-altman-meet-chipmakers-samsung-sk-hynix-execs-friday-sources-2024-01-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位知情人士称，OpenAI 首席执行官 Sam Altman 将于周五访问韩国，并会见芯片制造商三星电子和 SK 海力士的领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/openais-altman-meet-chipmakers-samsung-sk-hynix-execs-friday-sources-2024-01-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 22:23:53 GMT</pubDate>
